Detailed Description

This message is sent when a key is pressed longer than AXE_KEY_AUTOREPEAT_DELAY [ms] an will be repeated al AXE_KEY_AUTOREPEAT_INTERVAL [ms] args[0].t_byte[0] ... contains the key code of the key
